<div class=3D"description description6">
	<p>Many magnetic units are named for the people who discovered or invented=
 these ideas in our not so distant history. Learn more about them at the li=
nks below, listed in order of appearance.</p>
=09
	<div class=3D"inputitem gray">
		<div class=3D"KJpicc KJbigimg">
			<div class=3D"KJpic">
